ColumnDataMapperProvider
public class DefaultColumnDataMapperProvider
extends Object
implements ColumnDataMapperProvider

Default implementation. To add further mapping you should simply extend DefaultColumnDataMapperProviderHint and call addMapping(ColumnType, ColumnType, ColumnDataMapper) in the overridden DefaultColumnDataMapperProviderHint.addMappings(DefaultColumnDataMapperProvider) method.
